data.name: $FILE_ID
data.comment: {locked} This is the file ID for this localization file. This string value should not be used or translated.

data.name: loadComponentLog
data.comment: {Locked}A log message to show when a component starts loading. {0} is the component id, {1} is the component alias.

data.name: loadComponentEndLog
data.comment: {Locked}A log message to show when a component finishes loading. {0} is the component id, {1} is the component alias.

data.name: loadComponentRetryLog
data.comment: {Locked}A log message to show when loadComponent() is going to retry to load the component. {0} is the component id, {1} is the component alias, {2} is the current number of retry, {3} is the maximum number of retries.

data.name: loadPathDependencyLog
data.comment: {Locked}A log message to show when a path dependency starts loading. {0} is the path dependency name, {1} is the component id, {2} is the component alias.

data.name: isUndefinedValidateError
data.value: The value for "{0}" must not be undefined
data.comment: {Locked}Error to show when the Validate.isNotNullOrUndefined() is called on an undefined value. The {0} placeholder is the input's variable name.
